These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, onion
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, reading
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, satire
1. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the person eating onion##8
2. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | water      |
| Food          | onion | pineapple    |
| Hobby         | reading   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | satire      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, photographer
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, skateboard
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
3. the photographer is not to the right of the architect##8
4. the person driving the ship is not the person who's hobby is photography##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | juice        | soy-milk    |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks         | photography |
| Job         | photographer | architect   |
| Transport   | ship               | skateboard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, satire
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, indonesian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, fish
1. the spanish is in an odd position##4
2. the indonesian is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
3. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation       | satire |
| Music-Genre   | funk       | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | spanish | indonesian |
| Pet           | lizard        | fish   |

